{"tid":1352069,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚連登所有EE/Engine/HAM人 考電台牌啊","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:53:11.000Z","uid":242795,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb94a5d6a9f126a75b8f781c6dbfcaceac12c6dd","tid":1352069,"uid":242795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"業餘無線電（英語：Amateur Radio），也被稱作火腿電台（英語：ham radio）是一種供業餘無線電愛好者進行相互通訊、無線通訊技術實驗、自我訓練、個人娛樂、無線電運動（英語：Radiosport）、競賽（英語：Contesting）以及應急通訊（英語：Amateur radio emergency communications）的一項使用無線電頻率頻譜的無線電業務。其中「業餘無線電愛好者」指「經正式批准的、對無線電技術有興趣的人，其興趣純系個人愛好而不涉及謀取利潤」。業餘無線電與商業廣播、安全業務無線電或者其他專業雙向無線電（英語：Two-way radio）業務存在區別，業餘無線電並非這些專業無線電業務的業餘形式，也不是有關這些業務的業餘愛好，而是一項獨立的無線電業務。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">民防 救災用途都用得 你唔係唔學啊 有效距離超遠 架埋天線夠嗌去全球各地</span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">包括中國</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7a6532c7aad2a3a9cc9f96026c3727c15d10d8","tid":1352069,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:34:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"66c7d6c3182781fe87326163718658025f9de870","tid":1352069,"uid":39178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:42:03.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多啲detail，邊倒有得學同考<br />\n利申：EE仔"},{"pid":"043ea20879c29a0d7a2bf6fb46d55bba997843cb","tid":1352069,"uid":80966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9c9a7b2e452da83b75e8c26fc52669bf8673159","tid":1352069,"uid":242795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"043ea20879c29a0d7a2bf6fb46d55bba997843cb","tid":1352069,"uid":80966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:21:13.000Z","msg":"業餘電台牌照150蚊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/licensing/a201.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"htt